trans-unit.source: Represents a single item of data extracted from a workflow and all its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un elemento singolo di dati estratti da un flusso di lavoro e tutte le annotazioni associate.

trans-unit.source: When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a track point, it sends a tracking record to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Quando trova una corrispondenza per un track point, l'infrastruttura di rilevamento di runtime invia un record di rilevamento al servizio di rilevamento.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> may contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects that specify data to be extracted from the workflow and returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: Un oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> o un oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> può contenere oggetti <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> che specificano dati da estrarre dal flusso di lavoro e restituire nell'elemento <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> represents a single item of this extracted data in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Un oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> rappresenta un solo elemento di questi dati estratti nella proprietà <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> o nella proprietà <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the list of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene e imposta l'elenco delle annotazioni associate ai dati estratti.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" /> that contains the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Elemento <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection" /> che contiene le annotazioni associate ai dati estratti.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> can specify annotations to be sent with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Un oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> o un oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> può specificare annotazioni da inviare con i dati estratti

trans-unit.source: These are contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.Annotations%2A> property.
Gets or sets the extracted data associated with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta i dati estratti associati alla classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that represents the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Object" /> che rappresenta i dati estratti.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.Data%2A> contains the member data, specified by an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, that was extracted from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: La proprietà <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.Data%2A> contiene i dati dei membri, specificati da un oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, estratti dall'istanza del flusso di lavoro.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the property or field associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta il nome della proprietà o del campo associato ai dati estratti.

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the property or field that was extracted.
trans-unit.target: Il nome delimitato da punti della proprietà o del campo estratto.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure supports data extraction on fields and properties of classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; a member of such a field or property; and a single item of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface, for example a single element in a collection.
trans-unit.target: L'infrastruttura di rilevamento di runtime supporta l'estrazione dei dati su campi e proprietà di classi che ereditano dall'oggetto <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>, un membro di tale campo o proprietà e un elemento singolo di un campo o una proprietà (o un membro di un campo o una proprietà) che implementa l'interfaccia <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>, ad esempio un solo elemento di una raccolta.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A> contains the dot delineated name of the item extracted and is equivalent to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> depending on which type of extract specified the data contained by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
trans-unit.target: La proprietà <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A> contiene il nome delimitato da punti dell'elemento estratto ed è equivalente della proprietà <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>, a seconda del tipo di dati estratti specificato dalla classe <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
